Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.71,0:00:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.92,0:00:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watching Fairy Tail keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:10.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:20.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fighting on Galuna Island against Lyon and his gang who were scheming to resurrect Deliora,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but the great Erza came after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"The great?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu barged into the moon temple by himself and challenged Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for even more who-knows-what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:41.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The door to mystery is right in front of us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:44.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world's a wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:47.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,which we're already wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:52.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This excitement gets my heart racing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.24,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What is real, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.84,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I see tomorrow, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:10.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The only part leveling up is my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:15.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just throw away our daily life together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:23.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! S. O. W.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:29.27,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Living itself will be our training!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.27,0:01:32.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for even more who-knows-what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:40.82,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be satisfied with just the normal answers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This magical wonder life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.45,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future is wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:51.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do our best living our life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:53.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the way we want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wondering!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.77,0:02:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The city where I lived was attacked by Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even take a day for it to be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard the rumors, but I'd have never imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon, come over here! We've got a survivor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:59.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was saved by Ul and Lyon who just happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora... I won't forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora... One day I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And for me, that's how it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, sure you can keep up? {copy}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My training is harsh, you know. {copy}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll do anything! {copy}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:04:00.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can get the power to defeat Deliora, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'm ready for you anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Off with the clothes, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd strip in this snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I got it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll strip! All I gotta do is strip, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:31.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to control the cold, then you need to become one with the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything starts from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm t-totally used it already. {the multiple stutters make the subtitle hard to read. One is enough to illustrate his chattering teeth}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...he says while shivering...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to run, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, teach us magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and start running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm doing the basics, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:12.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the many magics, Creation Magic is the magic with the greatest freedom... {It may or may not be the magic that allows the greatest freedom, but a maker-magic wizard would certainly think it is}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each individual's Creation Magic is unique. {I think that't fine} {even though this is a sort of four kanji compound (fake, though, since it's not originally chinese), translating it with an expression like "Different strokes for different folks" or "Every man his own fortune" or something seems weird and out of place, so the literal meaning translation is probably best,IMO.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Devote yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And search out your own form...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:53.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have an extra pupil there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a rebel and quite the handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other one is named Lyon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them seem like they'll be future hunks. {Can't think of a better noun for a good-looking guy at the moment}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... When they grow up, let me have one, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take both of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their constant noise is driving me nuts. {"like everyday" makes Ul sound too much like a high school girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've got children, so no man'll come near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any love advice, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting any younger, Ul... {"ii toshi" usually means "you're plenty old enough"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:22.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be thinking about your own happiness a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think until we get better than Ul?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:29.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul's my goal! My dream is to beat her one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I've told you once, I've told you a thousand times, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so {\i1}dark{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're too cheerful and keep blabbing on about Ul all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me that the reason she accepted you as her pupil was that you were wrapped in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After seeing what I saw, how could I be not be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to drive away the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that myself... By my own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long... As long as I defeat Deliora, that's good enough for me. {putting "for me" at the beginning makes the sentence sound like "The Board of Redundency Board" mistake. I know it wasn't, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The minute I get the power, I'll say sayonara to that ice queen! {and since the previous sentence started with "as" I change this one so it wouldn't start with "as"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you call your teacher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you gonna teach me some powerful magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Creation Magic strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:43.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:46.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Creation Magic is the magic with the greatest freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:56.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find your own form, it can be as powerful as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying the same old stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stripping {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault I have this weird habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}my{\i0} fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hilarious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, pointy-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} shut up, droopy-eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you hear about Deliora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's moved to the Northern Continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:29.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere around Brago, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then peace has returned to Isvan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora is... at Brago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can win against Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for you, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to avenge my mother and father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave, and you're expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, then I'll haunt you for not teaching me more powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruins are... tilted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure how he did it, but only he would do something nuts like that. {wait, did I just make a horrible pun?  It's not intentional, I swear!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter whether he did it on purpose or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the light of the moon won't shine on Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:01.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew that his tendency for wanton destruction could actually come in handy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew. It was foreshadowed. {I don't get it either. It wasn't foreshadowed that I can see, and I tend to be on the lookout for such things. The line wasn't in the manga.}{wait, am I missing the joke here?  Is this a 4th wall breaking or...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found you, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't allow you to interfere with Reitei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:21.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon's followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to me! {You have another "things" a couple of lines later}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:30.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish things with Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:43.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! We're here, too, so just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:56.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know that Ul is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can stop him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Rose Garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... I didn't think it'd be this strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:01.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No questions. Just take Lyon away from here. {"ii kara" usually means, "just do what I as and don't ask questions"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:06.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's harder to fight when I have to protect you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out for the count.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't... able to do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:23.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:35.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A good friend of mine told me that I should start thinking about my own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:39.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't remember being all that unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:50.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With my two bright pupils growing day by day... Every day an adventure... {the semicolon just stood out for some reason}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the happiness I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:58.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to take back that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, your leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:05.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh this? I lost it, but it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:09.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Creation Magic is pretty amazing, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that monster is your darkness, then I have a reason to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:19.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go. I'll defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no one's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a hurdle to pass to take back my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake, Lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Gray-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:39.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:41.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:45.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, you're the strongest wizard there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd lose to some monster, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon, I've told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always someone better. {the more metaphorical/literal "there's an above to the above" or something like that doesn't seem to work in english...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a ton of wizards stronger than me in the countries to the west. {I think they're talking about the entire continent that Fiore is on}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the strongest, Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:08.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not then... why'd I go through all that training?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:12.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After you surpass me, then you should just find a new goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:17.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I became your pupil because I thought you were the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare lose to that monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't betray me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna be serious, then I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That pose... Where did you learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you wouldn't teach me any powerful magic, I had to read the spell books in your storehouse!  {I doubt people would misunderstand the "you forced me" but just to make sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you hide such powerful magic from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:51.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon! Did you read that book to the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who use that magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Lyon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What incredible magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It noticed us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No magic will work against Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll use this magic to trap you for eternity in ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you use that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul, why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use Iced Shell! {Iced Shell is good. But she doesn't want him to use it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who use it destroy their own bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:35.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that's the only thing that could stop this thing. {Although Iced Shell actually did defeat Deliora, nobody, including Ul, thought it could at the time. They thought it would just emprision it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that Lyon would think of trying the same thing I was going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was trying to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a disciple for you. {She didn't expect it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:47.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to get near my pupils!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for you, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:17.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic destroys the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic that turns one's own body into ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.05,0:16:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Lyon I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he knew that I became the ice, he'd probably spend his entire life trying to undo the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If he did that, that would defeat the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.48,0:17:01.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Lyon to see more of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you too, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:14.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, stop! Please, I'll do whatever you say from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live on as the ice, for all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth... to your future...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will seal your darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul gave her life to drive away my days of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:58.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Go forth... to your future..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:02.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With those words in my heart, I decided to start on a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Ul...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell, right? Ul did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul... What happened to Ul?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to surpass Ul now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:47.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry?! Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:19:00.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't challenged Deliora...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault, Gray.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, there's no end to this. {he's talking about the flashback! badabing!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give it up and surrender already, you pointy-eyed bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are pretty pointy themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:27.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.51,0:19:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:38.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, let me take this guy down. {I don't know why, but "take responsibility for him" doesn't sound right}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You already lost to him once, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some confidence you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault that Ul died ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurting my friends... Hurting the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:03.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to melt that ice... I can't forgive you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.54,0:20:07.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll punish you for them all, Lyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:12.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:14.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iced Shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:19.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ul cast the Iced Shell magic on this demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a demon that Ul risked her life to seal away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear? Ul is already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:30.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... have you gone mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return the villagers to the way they were,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:36.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,take your friends and leave this island immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last chance I will give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You think you can bluff me with that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:55.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:08.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many years pass, it won't change the fact that it's my fault Ul's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take responsibility sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been for the past 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Lyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:27.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we die together or live together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the guts to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:49.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Erza, everyone at Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:54.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm making my exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.74,0:22:02.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:05.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.94,0:22:15.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing after your profile left only in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.94,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You said, "I never want to see your face again," when you left me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:32.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the tears on your cheek said it all
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:38.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time you felt like you'd be swallowed up in the waves of contradiction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:45.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you always held back your tears, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.47,0:22:56.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"What a strong person," they said, but everyone overestimated you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:23:05.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and before you knew it you lost sight of who you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.15,0:23:09.33,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the sun I thought would always be near me collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.01,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the light shut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:16.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubbing out the truths and the lies of one day, altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.57,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry-go-round
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I greet the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:29.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,still, ironically, chasing after your profile in my revolving dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lectures!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:37.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we'll be teaching you the secrets of the Ice Wizard, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:41.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray uses Ice Creation Magic, and is always fighting with the fire-using Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're actually quite similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray gets lots of points for stripping off pretty much any clothing anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:51.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have a weakness for women's tears, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand, Bow, Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Gray have always fought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm not gonna lose to him, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:05.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:09.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm way stronger than that icey bastard, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.71,0:24:13.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray said pretty much the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Galuna Island, the Final Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:19.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who do you think is stronger, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:21.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it looks like Deliora is about to be resurrected! {Deliora is never actually resurrected. It's sort-of resurrected, and then it crumbles to pieces.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:24.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just trying to dodge the question!  Right...?
